@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hfpuew(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v0
    v0 = wp.exp((0.08 - (tmp + 0.14 + tmp + 0.32)))
    v0 = ((v1 + v2) / 0.27)
    v1 = wp.abs((0.46 * tmp))
    tmp = ((0.97 * wp.abs(v0 + 0.67)) / tmp)
    v2 = (tmp * wp.sin(0.11))
    v2 = (tmp - ((v2 + 0.52 / v2 + 0.62) * v1))
    data[tid] = v0
